{"type":"message","id":"5b69b9c1","parentId":"0a1aafd6","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:55:41.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a system cron job error notification. The cron job \"每日天气检查\" (Daily Weather Check) has been auto-disabled because it had 3 consecutive schedule errors, with the last error being \"invalid cron schedule: expr is required\".\n\nThis is an internal system message asking me to handle it internally. Since the user didn't explicitly ask me to fix this or relay this information, I should just handle it silently.\n\nLet me check if there's a cron configuration file or something I can look at to understand the issue. I should look at the workspace to find the cron configuration.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_znybwwolbmlb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"每日天气检查\" /workspace/projects --include=\"*.json\" --include=\"*.yaml\" --include=\"*.yml\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":33673,"output":298,"cacheRead":258,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773287722769}}
